{"tid":1797230,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東海戰線 日揆稱東海局勢不穩　日中關係不會真正改善","createTime":"2019-12-25T09:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T11:21:59.000Z","uid":165683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b1cb105eeda8c4b73c873c05d60cad5678937883","tid":1797230,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:03:23.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】日本首相安倍晉三對總理李克強表示，東海局勢不穩定，兩國關係不會真正有改善。<br />\n<br />\n安倍晉三與李克強在成都出席中日韓領導人會議後舉行雙邊會談。日本外務省公布，安倍晉三在會談中，指出東海局勢不穩定，日中關係不會真正有改善，他並且敦促李克強迅速解除中國對日本食品進口的限制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=374564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374564&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=72ca120d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374564&h=5d0243cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=374564</a>"},{"pid":"95cdc07777f08644b64c1b6fe391b2d0a726ae7e","tid":1797230,"uid":34757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:03:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06ae74134c09333f51cab5046bba365043d2bb22","tid":1797230,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:04:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解咁少人提鴻福堂？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【反修例】鴻福堂內地遭下架 最新聲明：堅決擁護一國兩制<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1561650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1561650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ELsOwk4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FELsOwk4.png&h=174e6f38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾百個港豬港女仲係咁tag fd買<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df88db4254f6d8855ee28ca1c94505a55c939f61","tid":1797230,"uid":120541,"like":2,"dislike":0